donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS
outputs.output_descr: The project is for the implementation of the Global Fund Round 5 TB Grant .  The objectives of the grant are: (i) To strengthen laboratory Services for diagnosis; (ii) To improve treatment outcomes by improving case management and support of tuberculosis patients and (iii) To develop and implement TB & HIV collaborative activities at all implementation levels

project_title: Strengthen National TB Control Program  ZIM-509-G08-T
